title: 'Product started malfunctioning after a week.'

I contacted Amazon they shared a couple of numbers for calling, however, that call landed with some financing company.  Amazon should stop selling the products whose warranty procedures are not clear. On the product, a year warranty is written but there is no way to claim it. This is misinformation.
